      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. BLUE CAT has been in good form, scoring three back at this track then placing twice in a row, most recently finishing second when she was prominent throughout over 1600m at this track. Finds a tougher race but she has the ability to test this field. 5. BLOOM NOSE turned in a fine effort to win by a neck at this track and distance last start in a much improved run. This looks a sterner test than last time but on his best form he is capable of another big performance. 4. KOTORINO SAEZURI missed the frame last time when fourth at this track. Prior to that had been in the money on two consecutive occasions. Form this track is hard to knock with two wins from five starts. Strong claims on her best form. 13. WING WIND made progress last time out, finishing second at the end of 1400m at this track. Best efforts measure up so capable of another big run.\",\"runners\":[2,5,4,13],\"exclusive\":false}",
